ABOUT

The Phoenicia Token project has been created with the intention to have a decentralized token for the Lebanese people, by the Lebanese people. The roadmap for this project is still currently unclear, as there hasn't been any major funding for this project. However, we will keep updating our social media as this project progresses into the future.

The Phoenicia Token - which represents the phoenix - symbolizes the rise of the phoenix from ashes, creating a portrait of the spirit of the Lebanese people, who always seem to thrive despite the country's hardships and dark history. Technically speaking, this token is a BEP-20 Compatible token type. For example you may add this token to Trust Wallet or MetaMask if you wish. It is also available on pancakeswap as well.
